#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1830
msgid "enum **PropertyHint**:"
msgstr "枚举 **PropertyHint**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1832
msgid "**PROPERTY_HINT_NONE** = **0** --- No hint for the edited property."
msgstr "**PROPERTY_HINT_NONE** = **0** —— 没有关于已编辑属性的提示。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1834
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_RANGE** = **1** --- Hints that an integer or float "
"property should be within a range specified via the hint string "
"``\"min,max\"`` or ``\"min,max,step\"``. The hint string can optionally "
"include ``\"or_greater\"`` and/or ``\"or_lesser\"`` to allow manual input"
" going respectively above the max or below the min values. Example: "
"``\"-360,360,1,or_greater,or_lesser\"``."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_RANGE** = **1** —— 提示整数或浮点型属性应在一个范围内，该范围通过提示字符串 "
"``\"min,max\"`` 或 ``\"min,max,step\"`` 指定。提示字符串可以选择包含 ``\"or_greater\"`` "
"和/或 ``\"or_lesser\"``，以允许手动输入分别超过最大值或最小值。例如： "
"``\"-360,360,1,or_greater,or_lesser\"``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1836
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_EXP_RANGE** = **2** --- Hints that an integer or float "
"property should be within an exponential range specified via the hint "
"string ``\"min,max\"`` or ``\"min,max,step\"``. The hint string can "
"optionally include ``\"or_greater\"`` and/or ``\"or_lesser\"`` to allow "
"manual input going respectively above the max or below the min values. "
"Example: ``\"0.01,100,0.01,or_greater\"``."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_EXP_RANGE** = **2** —— 提示整数或浮点型属性应在一个幂数范围内，该范围通过提示字符串 "
"``\"min,max\"`` 或 ``\"min,max,step\"`` 指定。提示字符串可以选择包含 ``\"or_greater\"`` "
"和/或 ``\"or_lesser\"``，以允许手动输入分别超过最大值或最小值。例如： "
"``\"0.01,100,0.01,or_greater\"``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1838
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_ENUM** = **3** --- Hints that an integer, float or string"
" property is an enumerated value to pick in a list specified via a hint "
"string such as ``\"Hello,Something,Else\"``."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_ENUM** = **3** —— "
"提示integer、float或string属性是枚举值，用于选择通过提示字符串，例如 "
"``\"Hello,Something,Else\"``，指定的列表。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1840
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_EXP_EASING** = **4** --- Hints that a float property "
"should be edited via an exponential easing function. The hint string can "
"include ``\"attenuation\"`` to flip the curve horizontally and/or "
"``\"inout\"`` to also include in/out easing."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_EXP_EASING** = **4** —— 提示应通过指数缓动函数编辑的一个float属性。提示字符串可以包括"
" ``\"attenuation\"``，以水平翻转曲线；和/或 ``\"inout\"``，以包括输入/输出缓动。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1842
msgid "**PROPERTY_HINT_LENGTH** = **5** --- Deprecated hint, unused."
msgstr "**PROPERTY_HINT_LENGTH** = **5** —— 不建议使用的提示，未使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1844
msgid "**PROPERTY_HINT_KEY_ACCEL** = **7** --- Deprecated hint, unused."
msgstr "**PROPERTY_HINT_KEY_ACCEL** = **7** —— 不建议使用的提示，未使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1846
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_FLAGS** = **8** --- Hints that an integer property is a "
"bitmask with named bit flags. For example, to allow toggling bits 0, 1, 2"
" and 4, the hint could be something like ``\"Bit0,Bit1,Bit2,,Bit4\"``."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_FLAGS** = **8** —— "
"提示一个整数属性是，具有命名位标志的，位掩码。例如，要允许切换位0、1、2和4，提示可能类似于 "
"``\"Bit0,Bit1,Bit2,,Bit4\"``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1848
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_LAYERS_2D_RENDER** = **9** --- Hints that an integer "
"property is a bitmask using the optionally named 2D render layers."
msgstr "**PROPERTY_HINT_LAYERS_2D_RENDER** = **9** —— 提示一个整数属性是，使用可选命名的2D渲染层的，位掩码。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1850
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_LAYERS_2D_PHYSICS** = **10** --- Hints that an integer "
"property is a bitmask using the optionally named 2D physics layers."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_LAYERS_2D_PHYSICS** = **10** —— "
"提示一个整数属性是，使用可选命名的2D物理层的，位掩码。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1852
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_LAYERS_3D_RENDER** = **11** --- Hints that an integer "
"property is a bitmask using the optionally named 3D render layers."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_LAYERS_3D_RENDER** = **11** —— "
"提示一个整数属性是，使用可选命名的3D渲染层的，位掩码。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1854
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_LAYERS_3D_PHYSICS** = **12** --- Hints that an integer "
"property is a bitmask using the optionally named 3D physics layers."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_LAYERS_3D_PHYSICS** = **12** —— "
"提示一个整数属性是，使用可选命名的3D物理层的，位掩码。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1856
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_FILE** = **13** --- Hints that a string property is a "
"path to a file. Editing it will show a file dialog for picking the path. "
"The hint string can be a set of filters with wildcards like "
"``\"*.png,*.jpg\"``."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_FILE** = **13** —— "
"提示字符串属性是文件的路径。编辑它会显示一个选择了该路径的文件对话框。提示字符串可以是一组带有通配符的过滤器，例如 "
"``\"*.png,*.jpg\"``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1858
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_DIR** = **14** --- Hints that a string property is a path"
" to a directory. Editing it will show a file dialog for picking the path."
msgstr "**PROPERTY_HINT_DIR** = **14** —— 提示字符串属性是目录的路径。编辑它会显示一个选择了该路径的文件对话框。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1860
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_GLOBAL_FILE** = **15** --- Hints that a string property "
"is an absolute path to a file outside the project folder. Editing it will"
" show a file dialog for picking the path. The hint string can be a set of"
" filters with wildcards like ``\"*.png,*.jpg\"``."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_GLOBAL_FILE** = **15** —— "
"提示字符串属性是项目文件夹外部文件的绝对路径。编辑它会显示一个选择了该路径的文件对话框。提示字符串可以是一组带有通配符的过滤器，例如 "
"``\"*.png,*.jpg\"``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1862
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_GLOBAL_DIR** = **16** --- Hints that a string property is"
" an absolute path to a directory outside the project folder. Editing it "
"will show a file dialog for picking the path."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_GLOBAL_DIR** = **16** —— "
"提示字符串属性是项目文件夹外部目录的绝对路径。编辑它会显示一个选择了该路径的文件对话框。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1864
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_RESOURCE_TYPE** = **17** --- Hints that a property is an "
"instance of a :ref:`Resource <class_Resource>`-derived type, optionally "
"specified via the hint string (e.g. ``\"Texture2D\"``). Editing it will "
"show a popup menu of valid resource types to instantiate."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_RESOURCE_TYPE** = **17** —— 提示一个属性是，一个 :ref:`Resource "
"<class_Resource>` 派生的类型的，一个实例，可以通过提示字符串（例如 "
"``\"Texture\"``）指定。编辑它会显示一个要实例化的有效资源类型的弹出菜单。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1866
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_MULTILINE_TEXT** = **18** --- Hints that a string "
"property is text with line breaks. Editing it will show a text input "
"field where line breaks can be typed."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_MULTILINE_TEXT** = **18** —— "
"提示字符串属性是带换行符的文本。编辑它会显示一个文本输入字段，可以在其中输入换行符。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1868
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT** = **19** --- Hints that a string "
"property should have a placeholder text visible on its input field, "
"whenever the property is empty. The hint string is the placeholder text "
"to use."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT** = **19** —— "
"提示每当字符串属性为空时，字符串属性应在其输入字段上，显示一个占位符文本。提示字符串是要使用的占位符文本。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1870
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_COLOR_NO_ALPHA** = **20** --- Hints that a color property"
" should be edited without changing its alpha component, i.e. only R, G "
"and B channels are edited."
msgstr ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_COLOR_NO_ALPHA** = **20** —— "
"提示应在不更改其alpha分量的情况下，编辑颜色属性，即仅编辑R、G和B通道。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1872
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_IMAGE_COMPRESS_LOSSY** = **21** --- Hints that an image "
"is compressed using lossy compression."
msgstr "**PROPERTY_HINT_IMAGE_COMPRESS_LOSSY** = **21** —— 提示使用有损压缩来压缩图像。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@globalscope.rst:1874
msgid ""
"**PROPERTY_HINT_IMAGE_COMPRESS_LOSSLESS** = **22** --- Hints that an "
